gobblin.async

Class AsyncRequest<D,RQ>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.async.AsyncRequest<D,RQ>
  • Type Parameters:
    D - type of data record
    RQ - type of raw request
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Request<RQ>

    public class AsyncRequest<D,RQ>
extends Object
implements Request<RQ>
    A type of write request which may batch several records at a time. It encapsulates the raw request, batch level statistics, and callback of each record
